  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Anthropic just shipped agent view in Claude Code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:09ed00f1283e53f09af6d77accf8143fccf334965a3539cb2d5ae507fb03d6cf",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "One list of every session you have running.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6f09506a74fb2ff1c99bf070a37b379633ed547f38a4d964f9f1a05f258e79bd",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 8
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Available today as a research preview. Before this, you juggled terminal tabs, tee-mux grids, and a mental ledger of who needed you next.",
      "checksum": "sha256:919e706749a044eb48351d51357903512f9973d729b67e53001d411fc4876424",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 8.126984126984127,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 16
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Now there is one place. 3 modes. 5 plans.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bae6258948ea43508a92c1afb6168673a3c89f9d5b279c828ad35ea98a11a1ff",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 39
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "First, see everything. Press the left arrow or run the claude agents command.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d546dd09d66761d8dba9b2baae27e94f547f6dd7023c2bfe7413be56ea12ad44",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 4.922630385487528,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 48
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Every row shows which sessions need you, which are working, and which are done.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8ea7305bcd00cd93b39c143878b1edc209f6e68075d64e0ff871f31eca70d5ca",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 61
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Second, peek and reply. Select a session to read the last turn.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c6e03b089cc1448e4b1eac8fe83d3e1f3e9ddf874db14e6ddc66c50e3f7bc817",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 75
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "If it is waiting on you, answer inline. Third, background anything.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e9df7e010dc415bb9f1fd1b5095d16d887d40d6afe162f0c8346f79a217f9f6a",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 4.08671201814059,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 87
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Use slash B G to push a running session into the view.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7e1addb6f1790a412f75920d43045ed313cf6506bb7aab83e921a4476156694e",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 98
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Or claude dash dash B G to start a fresh one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d74086d77e084b0aac22d301355df59b202a09c3b1fc28f4ce998424240e9e6f",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 110
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Here is how developers are using it. Dispatch several ideas at once and come back to pull requests ready for review.",
      "checksum": "sha256:899b23be00439e79d5883445b85b2dce2be384af6f1f5dcafd2eb8796cc8d7d2",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 6.408707482993197,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 121
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Babysit long running jobs that show their next run time right in the list.",
      "checksum": "sha256:eb43bbe7f9b55103c78bda1980ca5453f2ecc2af1e2816109298662ef169cf57",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.900952380952381,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 142
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Bounce between sessions with arrow keys without losing context.",
      "checksum": "sha256:481a2eafde576699abe9b721a661da1a09584c8cc3113954e246017ddbed4de5",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 156
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Scan status indicators to see what shipped.\n\nAgent view is available today on Pro, Max, Team, Enterprise, and Claude API plans.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a6b63f79c8f031dbe4f4823551deedd1dbd315e13645c44df788559a264e005a",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 8.126984126984127,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 165
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Opt in by running claude agents. If you want to learn more about AI, check out the dynamous dot A I community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ab1226c137467f25ecb1d77f44ecd07ba74155b6a54ef2db93f458f34a1f0aff",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 6.548027210884354,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 186
    }
  ]
